        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "没有枣核，门口的石子也凑数。七颗，挑圆的。他蹲下去，一颗一颗往尸背的衣褶里按——",
      "next": "n_hold"
    },
    "n_hold": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "zhenshi_step"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "playSfx",
          "params": {
            "id": "sfx_stone_press"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_doing"
    },
    "n_doing": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "按到第七颗，指尖底下那具尸轻轻一弹，像活人被人点了麻筋。他差点叫出声。",
      "next": "n_sig"
    },
    "n_sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_镇尸_石子",
            "signal": "zhenshi_stone_done"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_after"
    },
    "n_after": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（七颗。一颗都不能少。谁定的规矩？不知道。守就完了。）",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
